overview.en: DP is the only equity application token that represents users and developers in the entire Dolphin Wallte ecosystem. DP holders can have a variety of rights and interests in the Dolphin Wallet ecosystem. The total DP structure is 100 million pieces, and the ecological application is 100% stock market. The total stock market rating will be 90 million pieces, and the final circulation after deflation will be 10 million pieces, thus rewarding early developers and ecological users!
overview.zh: DP是Dolphin Wallte整个生态代表用户以及开发者唯一的权益应用型通证，DP持有者在Dolphin Wallet 生态中可以拥有多种权益。DP发型总量1亿枚，生态应用100%销毁，销毁总量应为9000万枚，最终通缩后流通量为1000万枚，以此来奖励早期开发者和生态用户！
